                    <p class="case-block-text-subtext short-length">A single scan contains dozens of sites, thousands of pages and millions of ads, cookies, and scripts. We architected navigation that allows a deep dive—and an easy way to come up for air.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="inner-block two-third float-left relative">
                  <img class="case-block-image" src="../images/tmt/scale1.svg" data-sr="scale up 20%" />
