            <section class="case-block case-full-image tmt-server"></section>
            <!-- END case-block -->

            <section class="case-block extra-padded tmt-gray">
              <div class="container">
                <div class="inner-block one-third absolute-right vertical-center mobile-padded-below mobile-container-absolute" data-sr>
                    <h2 class="case-block-text-heading short-length">The abstract,&nbsp;<br />made tangible</h2>
                    <p class="case-block-text-subtext short-length">The code that powers the web is dense and fast-moving. This object-oriented user experience helps users resolve problems more quickly.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="inner-block two-third float-left relative">
                  <img class="case-block-image absolute" src="../images/tmt/abstract2.png" data-sr="wait 0.75s, over 1s" />
                  <img class="case-block-image" style="position: relative; z-index: 100;" src="../images/tmt/abstract1.svg" data-sr="enter left, move 300px" />
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>
            <!-- END case-block -->

            <section class="case-block extra-padded tmt-white">
              <div class="container">
                <div class="inner-block one-third absolute-left vertical-center mobile-padded-below mobile-container-absolute" data-sr>
                    <h2 class="case-block-text-heading medium-length">21st century design&nbsp;<br />for 21st century threats</h2>
                    <p class="case-block-text-subtext short-length">To this day, many terminals are still in black and white—often out of necessity. We didn&rsquo;t use design just to &lsquo;pretty things up.&rsquo; It enhances user efficiency with smart use of color, tags, and symbols.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="inner-block two-third float-right" data-sr="enter right, move 200px">
                  <div class="frame frame-desktop shadow">
                    <img class="case-block-image" src="../images/tmt/timeline.jpg">
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>
            <!-- END case-block -->

            <section class="case-block-flex not-padded view-three-quarter">
                <div class="inner-block half float-left padded mobile-container-extra flex-center tmt-blue">
                    <h2 class="case-block-text-blockquote medium-length">Brave UX is a team of fearless experts...</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="inner-block half padded mobile-container tmt-gray flex-center">
                    <div class="container flex-col">
                        <img class="case-block-text-quote-icon align-left" src="../images/tmt/quote.svg" data-sr="enter top, move 75px">
                        <p class="case-block-text-quote medium-length">Brave UX is a team of fearless experts who can transform the most exhaustively complex tasks into an efficient and painless process. We came to the table with a powerful set of tools and they brought us a visionary approach to user experience and design. Brave showed us how a singular, cutting-edge product could extend our unparalleled capabilities and deliver more value from the smallest of IT teams to the most visited sites on the web.</p>
                        <p class="case-block-text-citation">Chris Olson, <em>CEO, The Media Trust</em></p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </section>
